- always put inside head element
-not visible to web user
-tell search engine about webpage
-use attribute to provide info

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title></title>

165 character description:
<meta name="description"content="x"/>

keyword search about webpage:
<meta name="keywords"content="x, y, z"/>

author search
<meta http-equiv="author"content="x" />

language search
<meta http-equiv="content-language" content="x"
for example, english would be en-us

</head>
<body>
<div>
/div>
</body>
</html>
